  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 7th level, you have mastered the ability to manifest dishes in the middle of battle, while under stress and duress.</p><p>As an action, you may spend a use of your Cooking Kit. When you do you gain the benefit of the Shinobi Snacks class feature as if you had completed a rest. When creating snacks using this feature, you can make a number of them equal to f your intelligence modifier. All willing creatures of your choice within 30 feet of you can be given a snack as if you had thrown it to them. You can use this feature once per long rest. </p><p>Beginning at 15th level, you can use this feature twice times per long rest.</p>",
